1 that are unexpended at the end of a fiscal year shall not revert but shall remain available to the
2 North Carolina Partnership for Children, Inc., to reallocate to local partnerships. Notwithstanding
3 G.S. 147-86.11 or any other provision of law to the contrary, the NCPC shall be allowed to hold
